stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> UNKNOWN

    UNKNOWN --> GOOD: Status VALID
    UNKNOWN --> SUSPENDED: Status SCHEDULED_OFFLINE<br>or PENDING_RENEWAL
    UNKNOWN --> BAD: Status REVOKED or EXPIRED

    GOOD --> UNKNOWN: PVACMS Unreachable<br>(status stale)
    GOOD --> SUSPENDED: Status SCHEDULED_OFFLINE<br>or PENDING_RENEWAL
    GOOD --> BAD: Status REVOKED or EXPIRED

    SUSPENDED --> GOOD: Status VALID (window opened<br>or renewal completed)
    SUSPENDED --> UNKNOWN: PVACMS Unreachable<br>(status stale)
    SUSPENDED --> BAD: Status REVOKED or EXPIRED

    BAD --> [*]: Connection torn down<br>(terminal — no recovery)
